DATATYPES IN JAVASCRIPT
we have 5 data types 
1.strings - this are made up of text e.g david 
2.boolean - this are true or false statementsn e.g true or false
3.number - this are numbers or integers e.g 1,2,3,4
4.null - an empty data 
5.undefined - an unspecified data types 

