FUNCTIONS IN JAVASCRIPT
A function is a reusable piece of code. 
it allows use to write a block of code once and use it anywhere we feel like it
is neccessary.
A function is created with a function keyword.
THINGS TO ESTABLIshABOUT A FUNCTION.
1.A varible not defined inside function must be declared as a parameter.
2.A function doesn't have the power to affect anything outside the scope,
unless it is called out.
3. A function must be called out by it's name with a bracket in front of it.

